<div class="container bg-white shadow-sm rounded p-4">
    <h1 class="my-4 text-center">Complaints Procedure Information</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">
      At <strong>Zytech Auto Parts</strong>, we are committed to providing quality products and excellent service. 
      However, we understand that sometimes things may not go as expected. 
      If you have a complaint, we take it seriously and aim to resolve the issue quickly and fairly.
    </p>

    <!-- How to Raise a Complaint -->
    <h4 class="mt-4">How to Raise a Complaint</h4>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Contact Us:</strong> In the first instance, please reach out to our customer service team by email or phone.</li>
      <li><strong>Provide Details:</strong> Share your order number, product details, and the nature of your complaint.</li>
      <li><strong>Investigation:</strong> Our team will investigate your complaint thoroughly and may request further information.</li>
      <li><strong>Resolution:</strong> We will provide you with a clear response and, where appropriate, corrective action or compensation.</li>
    </ol>

    <!-- Timeframe -->
    <h4 class="mt-4">Our Timeframe</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>We acknowledge complaints within <strong>24-48 hours</strong>.</li>
      {{!-- <li>We aim to provide a full response within <strong>10 business days</strong>.</li> --}}
      <li>If the matter is complex and requires more time, we will keep you updated on progress.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Escalation -->
    <h4 class="mt-4">Escalation</h4>
    <p>
      If you are dissatisfied with our initial response, you may escalate your complaint by contacting our 
      <strong>Customer Support</strong>. 
      We will conduct an independent review and provide a final resolution.
    </p>

